title: Howard Stern - March 31, 2015 [ALL-VERSIONS]
description:
Howard Stern - March 31, 2015

* Big Foot Game And Taylor Swift Arguments. 7:00am
* Scott Weiland & The Wildabouts Concert Coming Friday. 7:20am
* Dr. Leila Zucker Calls In. 7:30am
* Email, Viet Nam Debriefing And More. 8:00am
* John The Caller Vs. Bobo. 8:15am
* More Calls And Ralph Not Doing His Job. 8:35am
* Nicole Bass Update, Mr. Cancer Call And More. 8:40am
* Howard's Perfect Day. 8:50am
* Floating Doody Controversy. 9:00am
* Wolfie Interviews From A Bill Cosby Show. 9:10am
* What Does Howard Dread Most Bracket Interrupted By Shit Stories. 9:40am
* Robin's News. 10:05am
* Wrap Up Show - What You Need To Know And A Call. 11:15am
* Wrap Up Show - Josh Gad Sits In. 11:25am
* Wrap Up Show - Bathroom Habits. 11:40am

This includes an audio edit using @SternGeek's source.

This audio has been dyson compressed at 80% and amplified for minimum range. It
has a small amount of white noise mixed in to the final render to get rid of
those awkward silences that the MP3 format sometimes creates when there's not
enough volume to compress. Talk Radio & Podcasts sound much better, especially
thru earbuds, with this edit. You will also find it easier to hear audio details
in loud environments. If you have good speakers, or listen in a quite
environment, you don't need this. This encode should also use considerable less
power from your batteries
